{"tid":857502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"滴滴司機急用水樽「方便」 大陸仔誤飲人尿","createTime":"2018-10-11T06:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T09:32:12.000Z","uid":122,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b1aaef3a86317c9fe02944df60d19f0c64ac075a","tid":857502,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:42:05.000Z","msg":"到內地搭車的港人留意，不要亂飲車上飲品。日前內地一名孫姓男子與同事到上海公幹，期間透過平台召來滴滴專車。坐在前坐的孫先生因為口渴，喝了車內專車礦泉水，竟發現樽內的道竟是小便。<br />\n<br />\n孫先生表示，前日和4名同事到上海出差，當晚8時40分一起乘坐滴滴七座禮橙專車，從普陀區近鐵城市到樂坊精致廣場，他當時坐在前坐，因為口渴他喝了一口車裏配備的專車飲用水。惟一入口，孫先生即感覺不對，馬上吐出口中的「水」。孫先生直覺那是尿，質問司機下，對方亦承認。<br />\n<br />\n孫先生說，當時水樽上面貼有滴滴標誌，開蓋時，卻發現蓋子是鬆：「我當時和司機確認，因為裏面是滿的，司機說可能是上位乘客擰開沒喝。」<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳的影片所見，滴滴司機當時表示，天黑下自己看不到專用水，強調自己沒動過這瓶水。孫先生追問司機司機堅決否認尿是他的。孫先生當刻還表示：「這瓶水還有溫度。」<br />\n<br />\n孫先生表示，當自己準備打電話投訴，司機情緒開始激動，說自己會因此失業，繼而不停自責打自己，又向孫先生道歉，提議用錢私了。最終，孫先生致電滴滴並報警。<br />\n<br />\n滴滴公司昨晚回應，有關司機因內急找不到廁所，遂用礦泉水瓶方便，並將瓶子放置在前坐中控台，導致乘客誤飲。對於乘客遭遇，滴滴表示抱歉。昨日下午，工作人員已陪同乘客前往醫院進行身體檢查及跟進其健康情況。涉事司機因違背滴滴服務規則，已被平台封禁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181011/58781673\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181011%2F58781673&d=RVlam78G7dsTti9aOdoEZ0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=bf690635\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181011%2F58781673&h=c0cf1ae1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181011/58781673</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8171fcd57fab5ae3d2299f08347a5e04f7d216c4","tid":857502,"uid":54226,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/145157_837cb45e1e52249dfee5ee0d2020df73.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F145157_837cb45e1e52249dfee5ee0d2020df73.gif&h=3fe5e93a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02924bc9c00a1637fb8a3783a456140dae2a088a","tid":857502,"uid":60412,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:03:53.000Z","msg":"個蓋又開過又仲暖都仲飲，on99"},{"pid":"cc65704832a573faa465c1764a506d3c7b529fbe","tid":857502,"uid":199675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:05:41.000Z","msg":"害死個司機"},{"pid":"e4a9bc7601df4f6366345fb6454ff920e1412cce","tid":857502,"uid":9286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:06:49.000Z","msg":"飲之前一定聞到有尿味，除非佢個鼻壞撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51626532bd7bbdcea28440a21d8a6654adb4a35","tid":857502,"uid":40171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:09:47.000Z","msg":"成口一滴滴"},{"pid":"38b8be93e12a2518cf163bec5d629d026f605265","tid":857502,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"亂咁飲人野已經戇鳩"},{"pid":"b5d11dbb51840d279a246c980de77c17ec95a814","tid":857502,"uid":206089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:25:04.000Z","msg":"水同尿都分唔到 <br />\n<br />\n真係抵飲"},{"pid":"aad8f6ff9fa945035fbd604cf1d7762e21127135","tid":857502,"uid":146243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:29:12.000Z","msg":"條大陸仔自己想飲人啲尿仲想告人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4325811d37130a0c8091c726bf72b58c0b6011f","tid":857502,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T09:32:12.000Z","msg":"支那人都痴線，開過既野都敢飲<br />\n係咪咁貪小便宜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}